Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.85,0:00:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.62,0:00:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.33,0:00:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.26,0:00:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.94,0:00:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.75,0:00:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.59,0:00:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.96,0:00:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.06,0:01:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.27,0:01:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.60,0:01:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.04,0:01:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.75,0:01:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.22,0:01:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.72,0:01:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.84,0:02:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浪子不需要女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.61,0:02:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉我這種危險的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.54,0:02:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去找個老實可靠的男人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.63,0:02:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.96,0:02:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你討厭戴大耳環的女人,不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.63,0:02:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.84,0:02:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.31,0:02:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,謝謝妳給我美好的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.54,0:03:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混帳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.58,0:03:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#36  突來的親吻風暴!\N朱美的失戀物語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.73,0:03:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10點了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.90,0:03:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混帳傢伙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.38,0:04:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,因為我一個人搬不動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.55,0:04:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是,我看看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.22,0:04:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問…我可以碰她嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.72,0:04:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼可不可以的\N不碰她的話要怎麼搬呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.46,0:04:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.66,0:04:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.30,0:04:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,這樣我比較好搬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.98,0:04:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美真的好重喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.91,0:04:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.79,0:04:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?廣志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.66,0:04:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回到我身邊了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.10,0:04:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是啦,是我,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.64,0:04:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.84,0:05:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,就算妳喝醉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.54,0:05:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受託照顧別人的兒子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.44,0:05:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基於責任,不能讓妳隨便亂來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.15,0:05:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.56,0:05:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.70,0:05:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.50,0:05:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼,這是常有的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.27,0:05:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦,我的意思是\N我經常幫這種忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.34,0:05:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的嘴上有口紅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.57,0:05:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.57,0:06:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是被管理員親吻就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.74,0:06:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.80,0:06:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.50,0:06:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.20,0:06:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.14,0:06:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.17,0:06:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天有說了什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.51,0:06:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.08,0:06:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.78,0:06:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妳說喔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.48,0:06:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有我幫得上忙的地方\N我隨時都樂意幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.32,0:07:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子說話別說得這麼了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.89,0:07:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.33,0:07:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.46,0:07:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想當我的男朋友\N十年後再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.54,0:07:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才他的那番話\N似乎有什麼涵義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.58,0:07:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚我到底做了什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.72,0:07:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.43,0:07:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失戀了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.10,0:07:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.46,0:07:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果一顆電燈泡就能讓妳洩恨夠\N這樣實在算是便宜的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.64,0:07:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的男朋友跟五代長得很像嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.38,0:07:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.98,0:07:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以管理員,千萬不要介意喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.85,0:07:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是沒有在介意啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.95,0:08:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且,大家也已經不是被親個吻\N就可以吵鬧個半天的年紀了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.22,0:08:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.94,0:08:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,要去上班啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.68,0:08:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛這麼緊張啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.95,0:08:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.32,0:08:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要站在那邊發呆\N小心被車子撞到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.92,0:08:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.92,0:08:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個,送給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.06,0:08:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送給我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.20,0:08:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不需要了\N你嫌麻煩丟掉也無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.40,0:08:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會覺得麻煩啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.81,0:09:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她應該知道我已經戒煙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.75,0:09:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道,朱美喜歡我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.12,0:09:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.84,0:09:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,不要逞強了\N你不是戒煙了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.55,0:09:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.35,0:09:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說,你可別會錯意喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.42,0:09:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會錯意?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.52,0:09:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然在這裡\N我贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.83,0:09:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.63,0:09:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們賭了十圓\N賭五代會在什麼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.83,0:09:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才藏起來的是什麼東西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.87,0:09:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你無關的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.37,0:10:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代會不會放棄管理員\N改追朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.71,0:10:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們來賭個30圓吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.94,0:10:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶,我要賭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.31,0:10:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在胡扯什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.84,0:10:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.38,0:10:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.18,0:10:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,我們到旁邊\N好好地聊一聊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.12,0:10:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是五代你請客囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.55,0:10:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等,你們要聊什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.19,0:10:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來嘛,來嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.23,0:10:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,這裡是茶茶丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.07,0:10:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰打來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.74,0:10:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,打錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.01,0:10:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然叫我們儘快\N送兩碗豆皮蕎麥麵去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.68,0:10:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.33,0:10:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆,我出去買包煙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.13,0:10:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香煙?店裡明明就有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.90,0:11:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,接個電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.10,0:11:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.33,0:11:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住,不要逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.10,0:11:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.50,0:11:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請放心,這通電話是找我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.08,0:11:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.15,0:11:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您是哪位?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.62,0:11:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大致的情況我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.89,0:11:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的可以相信你嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.52,0:11:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的名片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.66,0:12:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷劍之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.46,0:12:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然寫成劍之介\N但請叫我五郎兵衛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.50,0:12:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人們都叫我“誠實的五郎”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.37,0:12:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有個請求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.40,0:12:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有信心能把你現在說的話\N正確無誤地傳達出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.77,0:12:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能請你寫封信?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.99,0:12:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不拜託你了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.26,0:12:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,說話一定要算話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.49,0:12:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少帳單一定要付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.24,0:12:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還在那裡耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.45,0:12:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他已經在那裡待一個小時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.42,0:13:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.59,0:13:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.66,0:13:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家裡又沒有能夠依靠的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.10,0:13:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,原來你在家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.95,0:14:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代也蠻行的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.52,0:14:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.45,0:14:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白痴,馬上就得意忘形起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.60,0:14:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.30,0:14:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.06,0:14:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此\N就是那個男的甩了朱美啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.84,0:14:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.67,0:14:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.80,0:14:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有這樣?\N不可能只有這樣吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.51,0:14:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只叫我跟朱美說\N他有來過這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.14,0:14:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道他想跟朱美復合嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.09,0:14:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明明已經決定忘了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.86,0:14:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是還忘不了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.00,0:14:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是很不甘願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.80,0:14:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次真的太扯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.30,0:15:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我果然受不了戴大耳環的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.04,0:15:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個壞男人\N那女人現在一定很…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.08,0:15:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼這麼說\N我特地回來好聲好氣懇求妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.68,0:15:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也不能沒有我,不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.76,0:15:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是喜歡妳這種個性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.69,0:15:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們去旅行一趟的話\N就能從另一種氣氛重新開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.93,0:15:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天晚上八點\N第五碼頭,渡輪乘船處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.27,0:15:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會等妳來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.15,0:15:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有在喝嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.15,0:15:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有在喝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.99,0:15:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這不叫喝酒,叫舔酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.73,0:15:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你接吻的事\N你還耿耿於懷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.83,0:16:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事不要在別人面前說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.50,0:16:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.40,0:16:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,我好羨慕你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.70,0:16:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次也請妳吻吻我唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.84,0:16:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了,前些時候我見到他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.81,0:16:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他好像叫廣志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.78,0:16:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎,他有說些什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.19,0:16:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我建議他寫了一封信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.56,0:16:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今還有什麼好寫的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.74,0:16:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是五代和小津江\N最近處得怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.57,0:16:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厲害\N居然不問五代和管理員的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.35,0:16:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪一邊還不都一樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.15,0:16:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陷在泥沼裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.32,0:16:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有進展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.45,0:16:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要你們管!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.72,0:17:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位,這裡有一鍋黑輪\N要不要吃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.13,0:17:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.56,0:17:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛好想吃黑輪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.16,0:17:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要菜頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.90,0:17:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有竹輪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.40,0:17:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很燙喔,小心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.34,0:17:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚,到後來怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.41,0:17:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟以往一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.08,0:17:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我當作下酒菜尋我開心\N鬧得天翻地覆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.45,0:17:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.08,0:17:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.09,0:17:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要出去旅行嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.99,0:17:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想出去散散心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.69,0:17:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.86,0:17:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起去?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.93,0:17:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.23,0:17:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看看你,馬上就當真起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.26,0:17:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.94,0:17:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她好像重新站起來了\N是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.11,0:17:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了,我也得走了\N我去上學了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.34,0:17:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.39,0:18:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你幫我拿行李
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.79,0:18:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的月台在對面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.69,0:18:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個還是還給妳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.80,0:18:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不太適合這種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.60,0:18:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更何況,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.30,0:18:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道,我知道\N對管理員的情義,對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.01,0:18:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二號月台的電車就快進站了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.34,0:18:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了安全起見\N請退到白線的後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.41,0:18:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電車來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.44,0:18:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,祝妳有個愉快的旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.85,0:18:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了安全起見\N請退到白線的後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.42,0:18:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然說這種可愛的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.94,0:20:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,這裡是一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.25,0:20:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.65,0:20:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.22,0:20:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也不在那裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.66,0:20:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,她什麼都沒跟我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.36,0:20:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到處都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.66,0:20:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說她要去旅行嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.76,0:21:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,她說想去散散心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.40,0:21:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,單獨去旅行嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.33,0:21:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.50,0:21:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,單獨去旅行的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.24,0:21:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能,朱美不可能自殺…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.81,0:21:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.21,0:21:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.81,0:21:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆,對不起喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.95,0:21:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.21,0:21:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳到底去哪裡了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.82,0:21:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼都聚在這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.08,0:21:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且,還安靜的這麼異常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.02,0:22:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連音樂都沒放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.36,0:22:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,工作了,工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.16,0:22:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要點什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.54,0:22:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好冷喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.21,0:22:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳煩不煩啊,冬天當然會冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.88,0:22:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,居然戴這麼大的耳環
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.47,0:23:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之瀨太太,請不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.14,0:23:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.74,0:23:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的太好笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.50,0:23:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好安靜喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.90,0:23:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對房客而言\N這是個無聊的星期天下午
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.57,0:24:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是在我的鏡子送來之後\N所發生的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.54,0:24:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.28,0:24:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「危險的變裝大會!\N響子也激烈大變身」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.55,0:24:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得我可憐的話\N就請讓我換回衣服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.56,0:24:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我們互相凝視時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.13,0:24:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會有一道奇妙的旋律\N在心中迴響著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.94,0:24:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法用言語來表達愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.68,0:24:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只好彈奏起了鋼琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.26,0:24:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請把夢丟進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.56,0:24:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為我測量一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:54.20,0:24:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛有多深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.10,0:25:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用輕觸的嘴唇演奏著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.31,0:25:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平靜的合聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.45,0:25:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使擁抱著妳依然惆悵滿懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.49,0:25:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢見了Fantasy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.70,0:25:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開啟了只有我們兩人\N才看得見的門扉Fantasy
